'''Princess of Theed''' was a title on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]]. It was the equivalent of being the [[Mayor/Legends|mayor]] of [[Theed/Legends|Theed]], the capital of the planet.

==Known persons to hold the position==
*[[Padmé Amidala/Legends|Padmé Amidala]] ([[34 BBY/Legends|34 BBY]]&ndash;[[33 BBY/Legends|33 BBY]]); later elected [[Monarch of Naboo/Legends|Queen of Naboo]]

